data.description: Welcome Home! This property has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and over 1,700 square feet of living space. The updated kitchen boasts slab granite countertops, tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, plenty of cabinets for storage and a dedicated breakfast area. The inviting living room is spacious & centered by a stone fireplace to keep you warm during the colder months! The primary bedroom has an en suite bath that features a soaking tub with a custom tiled surround, granite countertops, modern vessel sink and a walk in closet. Two additional bedrooms & an updated full bathroom round out the interior. Enjoy the very large, fully fenced backyard which offers a covered patio, rear carport and plenty of space for entertaining your guests! This home qualifies for 100% financing and does not require flood insurance. Call today to schedule your private tour!
